@startuml
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

actor "User" as User
agent "Market Data APIs\n(Finnhub/Yahoo/AlphaVantage)" as MarketAPI
agent "AI Providers\n(Groq/HF/Gemini)" as AIProviders
agent "Email/FCM Service" as NotifySvc
agent "Firebase/Local Store" as DataStore

rectangle "0.0 Vista Fin AI System" as System

User --> System : Login, transactions, queries, alerts
System --> User : Dashboards, advice, notifications

System --> MarketAPI : Price requests
MarketAPI --> System : Market data

System --> AIProviders : Prompts with context
AIProviders --> System : AI responses

System --> NotifySvc : Send OTP/alerts
NotifySvc --> User : OTP/alert messages

System <--> DataStore : Read/Write user data
@enduml
